### =========================
### LOGIN TEACHER
### COPY TOKEN FROM RESPONSE
### =========================

POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher1@gmail.com",
  "password": "1234"
}


### =========================
### DASHBOARD (USE TOKEN)
### =========================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/dashboard/stats
